{"tid":1144991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦出線又點？攞歐聯都係黑返嚟㗎,屌你老母！","createTime":"2019-05-08T11:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T11:59:35.000Z","uid":43785,"like":45,"dislike":212,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"8d22f1cff3a59c36e9739210cf98986674ba2459","tid":1144991,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:46:04.000Z","msg":"全場波咁多人招呼美斯一個,<br />\n為咗報仇,踢到打mma咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3opsm7H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3opsm7H.gif&h=15e31511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢件食屎狗一早應該紅牌啦屌你老母。<br />\n決賽唔畀出場。<br />\n<br />\n入波有冇睇var呀,有兩球疑似越位㗎。<br />\n<br />\n仲有嗰球角球根本就犯曬規。<br />\n掉界外球都要過後腦喇， <br />\n開波有冇舉手呀仆街，我屌你老母扮換人。<br />\n開波識唔識得行返出條底線呀。<br />\n<br />\n罰球唔岩位，都成日要重開啦，<br />\n球證應該一早要吹佢重開角球， 唔可以咁狗。<br />\n球證應該行出嚟道歉。<br />\n<br />\n今場根本就係黑哨。<br />\n今次終於輪到我地巴塞講「北京電視機」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca4e2f65f79d494428d8bace6774a69bd9f2acc","tid":1144991,"uid":248072,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"55<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757109fa5a6a6d566700120d545db6921d4ec18a","tid":1144991,"uid":11254,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:47:30.000Z","msg":"係 仲要嘈住我地巴塞球員訓教<br />\nSEND左EMAIL叫佢重賽了"},{"pid":"f93b005548ca3a1772cbe40484378b91d20bdf3d","tid":1144991,"uid":138459,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mJ8Q5t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mJ8Q5t.png&h=e4dc65c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4rN6DP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4rN6DP.png&h=b0ce7613&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FzjoEYQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFzjoEYQ.png&h=2f543